## Failure Handling & Rollback

### If AWS Provisioning Fails
```bash
# Rollback command (idempotent)
aws secretsmanager delete-secret --secret-id "runner/*" --force-delete-without-recovery
aws kms schedule-key-deletion --key-id alias/runner-credentials --pending-window-in-days 7

# Then re-run provisioning script
bash scripts/operator-aws-provisioning.sh
```

### If Worker Provisioning Fails
```bash
# Rollback command
ssh akushnir@192.168.168.42 'sudo systemctl stop vault-agent node_exporter'

# Service binaries remain (idempotent to reinstall)
scp scripts/provision/worker-provision-agents.sh akushnir@192.168.168.42:/tmp/
ssh akushnir@192.168.168.42 'sudo bash /tmp/worker-provision-agents.sh'
```

### If GCP Provisioning Fails
```bash
# Rollback command
gcloud secrets delete runner-* --quiet --project=elevatediq-runner
gcloud iam service-accounts delete runner-watcher@elevatediq-runner.iam.gserviceaccount.com --quiet

# Then re-run provisioning script
bash scripts/operator-gcp-provisioning.sh --project elevatediq-runner
```

